{"tid":1512070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰員工肯企出黎未？","createTime":"2019-08-27T17:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T10:30:52.000Z","uid":31773,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f35deb0ff70df439f362b44ee185f50c742d89cb","tid":1512070,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:31:33.000Z","msg":"如果閣下貴為一名國泰員工<br />\n<br />\n你亦曾經自豪自己係香港航空公司既員工<br />\n<br />\n咁你好應該企出黎對抗白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n如果你話公司怕無左個中國領空而跪低<br />\n<br />\n我相信公司更怕同時間無左你地而跪低<br />\n<br />\n因為員工一定係公司重要資產<br />\n<br />\n試問一間公司點可以無啦啦變幾百或幾千人頂替你地，就算要Training 都要時間<br />\n<br />\n你睇下台灣長榮年年搞罷工幾齊心<br />\n<br />\n而長榮佢地為錢咋，你地今次係為自由而企出黎，自由何價？<br />\n<br />\n唔好話怕無左份工，我相信因為企出黎而失業，一定好多香港人支持你<br />\n<br />\n而要經濟援助我都第一個支持<br />\n<br />\n所以懇請各位國泰員工好企出黎為自由發聲<br />\n<br />\n手段好簡單<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工&gt;無限期罷工&gt;集體辭職</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日國泰，他日就全港企業</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a81dde43af35b4a17c58260b4af9811983dc2622","tid":1512070,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f17c14afd71a965e78076da718f26b008e89c2","tid":1512070,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e8fd449c7e1b68296efbc508fc296c1ea191f8","tid":1512070,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a334644c46ff24b09ccb4cebe9748675b6dcc06f","tid":1512070,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor